{"tid":1482203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［人民日報今朝妄想扭轉輿論] 真相来了！#香港爆眼女事件四大谜团逐个解开#","createTime":"2019-08-18T04:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T04:26:54.000Z","uid":249040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c3232eef237974f027d0377ccb20c472dd0ec361","tid":1482203,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:23:33.000Z","msg":"睇下人民日報今朝八點報道<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4406555976093076\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2Fstatus%2F4406555976093076&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPBzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=4703e519\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/status/4406555976093076</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">spin到 「黑衣還眼」<br />\n試想下如果一輸，<br />\n點生活係呢個顛倒是非黑白、只為弄權嘅社會？<br />\n<br />\n如果818遊行受訪 講番原因係因為受傷女義士，就會被呢篇報導壓制左個輿論發酵種子。大陸人一定唔信。咁你話 關香港人咩事？留意番內文張長圖 係繁體字， 所以家中長輩、中間派都係高危。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">We can be fire, we can be water.<br />\nToday is the day,<br />\nWe declare our freedom of will, in choosing always the right actions.<br />\nAnd the world will never be the same.<br />\nWe show how we live in a higher way of civilisation.<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"5ee3be7b442181856fd1ee6f786ab6340dfb0f99","tid":1482203,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:24:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df2967ed8daa104259c24c013b5a0b6bf647a8ae","tid":1482203,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:25:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a038589510f6b68a7f001af0f7620b08d92404be","tid":1482203,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:26:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb777290420040db4b5421ccbb51497e39c469e2","tid":1482203,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:26:54.000Z","msg":"推"}]}